en_29699_0	One more awareness programme, lectured by Army Officers to educate Station Masters of the Sri Lanka Railways (SLR) department about current security concerns and precautionary measures got underway on Tuesday (9) at Tripoli premises of the SLR.
en_29699_1	40 station masters of the SLR gathered there.
en_29699_2	Lieutenant Colonel M. B. B. N Herath, General Staff Officer 1 Coordination of the 14 Division educated the attendees on the subject.
en_29699_3	This lecture was conducted on the directions of the General Officer Commanding, 14 Division.
en_29699_4	Meanwhile, the same lecture was repeated on Wednesday (10) at the same venue for 30 more station masters as the second stage of the lecture sessions.
